\c 13
\s UDavida ufisa ukuletha umtshokotsho wesivumelwano eJerusalema
\p
\v 1 UDavida wasecebisana lezinduna zezinkulungwane lezamakhulu laye wonke umphathi.
\v 2 UDavida wasesithi ebandleni lonke lakoIsrayeli: Uba kulungile kini, njalo kuvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wethu, kasisabalale sithumele kubafowethu abaseleyo emazweni wonke akoIsrayeli lakubapristi lamaLevi alabo emizini, emadlelweni, ukuze babuthane kithi\x + 1 Sam. 31.1.\x*.
\v 3 Besesibuyisa kithi umtshokotsho wesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu wethu, ngoba kasiwudinganga ensukwini zikaSawuli\x + 15.13. 1 Sam. 7.1,2. 2 Lan. 1.5.\x*.
\v 4 Ibandla lonke laselisithi kwenziwe njalo, ngoba udaba lwalulungile emehlweni abo bonke abantu.
\v 5 UDavida wasebuthanisa uIsrayeli wonke\x + 15.3. 2 Sam. 6.1.\x* kusukela eShihori yeGibhithe\x + Josh. 13.3. Jer. 2.18. Nani 34.5.\x* kuze kube sekungeneni kweHamathi\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x* ukuletha umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu usuka eKiriyathi-Jeyarimi\x + 1 Sam. 6.21. 7.1. Josh. 9.17.\x*.
\v 6 UDavida loIsrayeli wonke basebesenyukela\x + 2 Sam. 6.2-11.\x* eBhahala\x + Josh. 15.9.\x*, eKiriyathi-Jeyarimi eyakoJuda, ukuze benyuse lapho umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu iN\nd kosi\nd*, ehlala \add phakathi\add* \w kwamakherubhi\w** phezu kwawo, lapho ibizo elibizwa khona\x + 2 Sam. 6.2.\x*.
\v 7 Basebewuthwala umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu ngenqola entsha bewususa endlini kaAbinadaba; njalo oUza loAhiyo babetshayela leyonqola.
\v 8 UDavida loIsrayeli wonke babedlala-ke phambi kukaNkulunkulu ngamandla wonke, langengoma, langamachacho\x + 15.16.\x*, langezigubhu zezintambo\x + 15.16.\x*, langezingungu, langezinsimbi ezincencethayo, langezimpondo\x + 15.16.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Lapho befika ebaleni lokubhulela likaKidoni, uUza welula isandla sakhe ukubamba umtshokotsho, ngoba inkabi zakhubeka.
\v 10 Ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaselumvuthela uUza, yamtshaya, ngenxa yokuthi welulela isandla sakhe emtshokotshweni; wasefela khonapho phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Levi 10.2. 2 Sam. 6.7.\x*.
\v 11 UDavida wasethukuthela ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* imfohlele ngokufohla uUza; waseyibiza leyondawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiPerezi-Uza, kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 12 UDavida wasemesaba uNkulunkulu ngalolosuku, esithi: Ngizawuletha njani kimi umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu?
\v 13 Ngakho uDavida kawulethanga umtshokotsho kuye emzini kaDavida, kodwa wawuphambulela endlini kaObedi-Edoma umGithi.
\v 14 Ngakho umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu wahlala kwabendlu kaObedi-Edoma endlini yakhe inyanga ezintathu. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibusisa indlu kaObedi-Edoma lakho konke ayelakho\x + 26.5. 2 Lan. 25.24.\x*.
